name: The summit of mount zebra, on planet serenity
description:
Zebras are wild and graceful animals. They symbolize freedom, individualism and harmony. In times of madness and economic interests this totem is welcome. James webb will find this place?
Imagination often takes us to worlds that never were, but without it we go nowhere. (Carl Sagan).
The James Webb telescope is now in place. Arrange your mirrors and prepare each device to start seeing beyond. Authentic cosmic beauties await us in inhospitable regions, closer to the past.
How do you imagine these unknown worlds?
